Hi Li,

I have already accepted an internship offer from Lucy Cherkasova from HP
Labs. I will be there over the summer and would love to meet you some time.

Sorry for the delayed response.

Thanks a lot.
-Abhishek.

On Mon, Feb 22, 2010 at 11:22 AM, Li, Jun (HP Labs) <jun.li@hp.com> wrote:
Hi Abhishek,

I received your resume from your application to the HP Labs summer
internship on cloud service development (Req. 385468).  I am the researcher
who is responsible for this research effort.  I would like to see whether
you are available this week so that I can have a phone interview with you.
If you have time conflict this week, we can arrange the phone interview to
early next week. To better match my schedule, could you send me two or
three your available time slots? The interview will allow me to explain to
you the project here at HP Labs and understand your background and research
interest and it will be about one hour.

I am looking forward to speaking with you soon.

Regards,

Jun



